    <h2 id="identity-heading"><span aria-hidden="true">&#127987;&#65039;&#8205;&#127752;</span> Identity</h2>
    <p>As an Asian New Zealander, queer, and neurodivergent woman, I bring a unique perspective that shapes how I
      approach design. I notice the details, am always questioning "why?", and care deeply about making designs that
      truly include everyone.</p>
  </section>

  <section class="card" aria-labelledby="hobbies-heading">
    <h2 id="hobbies-heading"><span aria-hidden="true">&#129505;</span> Hobbies</h2>
    <p>Outside of design, I also enjoy channeling my creativity into drawing, cosplay, and baking. Other things that
      bring me joy include: being around animals and in nature, playing video/board games, reading, ice skating, and
      munching on a good crunchy snack :)</p>
  </section>

